- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper involves the use of a machine learning algorithm to classify skin diseases.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a potential sub-category as the developed Android application involves interaction between humans and technology.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with image processing and classification.
